<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_73_r1l14"><expan>D<ex>er</ex></expan> Priorin vnd <expan>Co<ex>n</ex>uent</expan> <expan>gemeinlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> deʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l15">frawen <expan>kloſt<ex>er</ex>s</expan> cʒü ſant Marks cʒü <expan>VVircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_73_r1l16">Erſamen geiſtlıchen / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von Jacob Toplers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l17"><expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / nymt vns ſelcʒeim / daʒ Jr vns in ſölıcher maſʒe vnd geleich </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l18">als entſagens vveıſe ſchreıbet / vnd mainten vvir <expan>ſolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des müglıch von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l20">ew <expan>v̈berhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein / wan Jr 
<add><ab facs="#facs_73_r1l19">vns </ab></add> vormals nichts davon <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> noch er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l21">ynnert habt / . Auch ıſt derſelb vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit nicht anheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l22">vnd vvenn er herheim kümt / ſo wöllen vvir Jn 
<del rend="strikethrough">do </del> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒered </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l23"> <expan>ſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd ew 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan></del> ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> vviſſen laſſen / ob die <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l24"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> an vns <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> /. Beſunder het Jr cʒü <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l25"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ıht <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Darvmb <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l26">mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> <expan>ſlewnige<ex>n</ex></expan> rechten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> helffen / wenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l27">vvir des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> / ſo <expan>dıſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü den Jr <expan>cʒeſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l28">anheim ſind / . wolt 
<del rend="strikethrough">vns </del> <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> darüber <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> recht 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſchaden </del> vns <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l29">den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ſchaden 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒücʒiehen </del> darvmb cʒücʒiehen / So <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtünde<ex>n</ex></expan> wir vvol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l30"> daʒ 
<del rend="strikethrough">wir </del> das <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew dargieng / vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des cʒü ew <expan>gewart<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_73_r1l31">geſcheh vns daran von ew vngütlıch / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Erhardȷ . x<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_73" id="36r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>D<ex>er</ex></expan> priorin und <expan>co<ex>n</ex>vent</expan>
<expan>gemeinlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dez frawen
                            <expan>klost<ex>er</ex>s</expan> czü sant Marks czü
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamen geistlichen, als ir uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        habt von Jacob Toplers, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, nymt uns
                        selczeim, daz ir uns in sölicher masze und geleich als entsagens weise
                        schreibet und mainten, wir <expan>solt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des müglich von ew
                                <expan>überhab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein, wan ir <add>uns</add>
                        vormals nichts davon <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> noch erynnert habt.
                        Auch ist derselb unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> czü
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit nicht anheim, und wenn er herheim
                        kümt, so wöllen wir in <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czered <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan> und ew
                        ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wissen lassen, ob die
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> an uns <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan>.
                        Besunder het ir czü <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>n</expan> iht <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        darumb <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ew <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheimbot<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mit <expan>ewre<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>volle<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalte <expan>unv<ex>er</ex>czogen</expan>
<expan>slewnige<ex>n</ex></expan> rechten <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
                        helffen, wenn wir des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so
                                <expan>diselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, czü den ir
                            <expan>czesprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt, anheim sind. Wolt
                                <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> darüber <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        recht uns <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        schaden darumb czücziehen, so <expan>v<ex>er</ex>stünde<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir wol, daz das <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew dargieng und gescheh uns
                        daran von ew ungütlich. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Erhardi x<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
